			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">See the difference instantly.</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-white/70">
				Drag the slider to compare squeezed vs desqueezed with a cinematic look applied.
			</p>

			<div class="mt-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-4 md:p-6">
				<div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black" data-ba-root>
					<div class="aspect-[16/9]">
						<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/15 to-white/0"></div>
						<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-25 [background:radial-gradient(80%_60%_at_50%_30%,rgba(255,106,0,0.18),transparent_60%)]"></div>
						<div
							class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat"
							style="background-image:url('/images/before-after/after-desqueezed-lut.png')"
							data-ba-after
							aria-label="After: desqueezed with LUT applied"
						></div>
						<div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-1/2 overflow-hidden" data-ba-before>
							<div
								class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat"
								style="background-image:url('/images/before-after/before-squeezed.png')"
								aria-label="Before: squeezed"
							></div>
							<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(120deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.06),rgba(255,255,255,0.00))]"></div>
						</div>
						<div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-white/50 cursor-ew-resize" data-ba-divider></div>
						<button
							class="absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full border border-white/30 bg-black/40 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white/90 backdrop-blur cursor-ew-resize transition-[box-shadow,border-color,background-color] hover:border-[#FF7A1A]/45 hover:bg-black/55 hover:shadow-[0_0_0_4px_rgba(255,122,26,0.12)] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#FF7A1A]/30"
							type="button"
							aria-label="Drag slider"
							data-ba-handle
						>
							Drag
						</button>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
					<div>
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/90">Before / After</p>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/70">
							Real frames: squeezed capture vs desqueezed output with a cinematic look applied.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div id="trust" class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-start gap-6 text-sm text-white/45 md:justify-end">
						<span class="font-semibold tracking-wide">ARRI</span>
						<span class="font-semibold tracking-wide">RED</span>
						<span class="font-semibold tracking-wide">Blackmagic</span>
						<span class="font-semibold tracking-wide">Panasonic</span>
					</div>
				</div>
		</section>

		<section id="faq" class="border-t border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02]">
			<div class="page-shell py-16 md:py-24">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-3xl">FAQ</h2>
				<div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/40 p-6">
						<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">Do I need an NLE?</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/70">
							No. Use the suite for monitoring, capture, and live looks. Editorial can stay in the tools they already use.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/40 p-6">
						<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">Does it support common anamorphic ratios?</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/70">
							Yes—common squeeze factors and custom math for unusual lenses.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/40 p-6">
						<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">How do exports hand off to editorial?</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/70">
							The apps are designed around clean export paths, preserving geometry and look intent for the next stage.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/40 p-6">
						<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">Is this optimized for mobile and tablets?</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/70">
							Yes—responsive layout, performance-first media, and reduced-motion support.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="contact" class="border-t border-white/10 bg-black">
			<div class="page-shell py-16 md:py-24">
				<h2 class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Contact us</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-white/70">
					Questions, feedback, a bug report, or want to collaborate? Send a message and we’ll reply by email.
				</p>
				<div class="mx-auto mt-4 flex max-w-2xl flex-wrap items-center gap-3 text-sm text-white/65">
					<span class="text-white/50">Or email us directly:</span>
					<span class="font-semibold text-white/85" data-direct-email>teamcentersap@gmail.com</span>
					<button
						type="button"
						class="inline-flex h-8 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 text-xs font-semibold text-white/75 hover:bg-white/[0.06] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/20"
						data-copy-email
					>
						<svg class="hidden h-4 w-4 text-white/80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" data-copy-check>
							<path
								d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"
								stroke="currentColor"
								stroke-width="2"
								stroke-linecap="round"
								stroke-linejoin="round"
							/>
						</svg>
						<span data-copy-label>Copy</span>
					</button>
					<span class="sr-only" aria-live="polite" data-copy-status></span>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-10">
					<form
						class="mx-auto max-w-2xl rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6"
						data-contact-form
						novalidate
					>
						<div class="grid gap-4">
							<label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white/80">
								Name
								<input
									class="h-11 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-4 text-sm text-white outline-none focus:border-white/25"
									type="text"
									name="name"
									required
									autocomplete="name"
								/>
							</label>
							<label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white/80">
								Email address
								<input
									class="h-11 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-4 text-sm text-white outline-none focus:border-white/25"
									type="email"
									name="email"
									required
									autocomplete="email"
									inputmode="email"
									aria-describedby="email-error"
									data-contact-email
								/>
								<span id="email-error" class="text-xs font-medium text-[#ff6a00] hidden" data-email-error>
									Please enter a valid email address.
								</span>
							</label>
							<div class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white/80">
								<span id="topic-label">Topic</span>
								<input type="hidden" name="topic" value="Collaboration" data-topic-input />
								<div class="relative">
									<button
										class="flex h-11 w-full items-center justify-between rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-4 text-left text-sm text-white outline-none transition focus:border-white/25 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/10"
										type="button"
										aria-haspopup="listbox"
										aria-expanded="false"
										aria-labelledby="topic-label"
										data-topic-trigger
									>
										<span class="font-semibold text-white/90" data-topic-value>Collaboration</span>
										<svg class="h-4 w-4 text-white/60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
											<path d="M7 10l5 5 5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
										</svg>
									</button>

									<div
										class="absolute left-0 right-0 z-20 mt-2 hidden overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/95 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.7)] backdrop-blur"
										role="listbox"
										aria-labelledby="topic-label"
										data-topic-list
									>
										<button
											type="button"
											role="option"
											class="flex w-full items-center justify-between px-4 py-2.5 text-left text-sm text-white/90 hover:bg-white/5"
											data-topic-option="Collaboration"
										>
											<span>Collaboration</span>
										</button>
										<button
											type="button"
											role="option"
											aria-selected="false"
											class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 text-left text-sm text-white/85 hover:bg-white/5"
											data-topic-option="Technical support"
										>
											Technical support
										</button>
										<button
											type="button"
											role="option"
											aria-selected="false"
											class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 text-left text-sm text-white/85 hover:bg-white/5"
											data-topic-option="Bug report"
										>
											Bug report
										</button>
										<button
											type="button"
											role="option"
											aria-selected="false"
											class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 text-left text-sm text-white/85 hover:bg-white/5"
											data-topic-option="Press / media"
										>
											Press / media
										</button>
										<button
											type="button"
											role="option"
											aria-selected="false"
											class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 text-left text-sm text-white/85 hover:bg-white/5"
											data-topic-option="Other"
										>
											Other
										</button>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white/80">
								Message
								<textarea
									class="min-h-32 resize-y rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white outline-none focus:border-white/25"
									name="message"
									required
									maxlength="2000"
									placeholder="Tell us what you’re trying to do, device, and what you’re seeing."
								></textarea>
								<span class="text-xs font-medium text-white/45">Max 2000 characters.</span>
							</label>
						</div>

						<div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
							<button
								class="inline-flex h-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white px-6 text-sm font-semibold text-black hover:bg-white/90 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/40"
								type="submit"
							>
								Send
							</button>
							<p class="text-xs text-white/50" data-contact-status></p>
						</div>
					</form>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<SiteFooter />

	</main>

</Layout>

